## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="da6a9-102"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.Hosting.IMemoryCacheManager>接口由主机环境（如 ASP.NET）实现，并由 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> 必须与主机环境交互以确定内存使用情况的实现使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="da6a9-102">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.Hosting.IMemoryCacheManager> interface is implemented by host environments such as ASP.NET, and is consumed by <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> implementations that must interact with the host environment to determine memory usage.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="da6a9-103">由于缓存通常会消耗大量内存，因此 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.Hosting.IMemoryCacheManager> 接口可帮助主机环境管理内存使用情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="da6a9-103">Because caches often consume significant quantities of memory, the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.Hosting.IMemoryCacheManager> interface helps host environments manage memory usage.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="da6a9-104">通常，只有 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> 管理内存中缓存对象的实现才能使用此接口。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="da6a9-104">Typically, only <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> implementations that manage cache objects in memory would use this interface.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
